  <Overview>DoChat(&#x76D2;&#x88C5;&#x5FAE;&#x4FE1;) is a Dockerized WeChat(&#x5FAE;&#x4FE1;) PC Windows Client for Linux.&#xD;
&#xD;
WeChat PC will be started on your Linux desktop by running the following one-line command:&#xD;
&#xD;
